{"tid":1519786,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有合理懷疑對家用緊呢招！","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:02:12.000Z","uid":312395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3453387236d4037942417116be04363cabb6f3","tid":1519786,"uid":312395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"曹劌論戰 - 左傳<br />\n<br />\n原文<br />\n<br />\n既克，公問其故。對曰：「夫戰，勇氣詞解也。一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭。彼竭我盈，故克之。夫大國難測也，懼有伏焉。吾視其轍亂，望其旗靡詞解，故逐之。」<br />\n<br />\n譯文<br />\n<br />\n打敗齊軍後，魯莊公問當中原因。曹劌回答說︰「作戰，靠的是勇氣。第一次擂鼓士氣振作，第二次擂鼓，士氣就有些衰退，第三次擂鼓，士氣就耗盡了。他們的士氣耗盡而我軍士氣旺盛，所以能戰勝他們。齊國強大，一時難以猜測齊軍是否敗走，恐怕他們埋下伏兵。我察看他們的車轍混亂，看到他們的旌旗倒下，所以追擊他們。」<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://rthk9.rthk.hk/chiculture/chilit/dy01_0205.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frthk9.rthk.hk%2Fchiculture%2Fchilit%2Fdy01_0205.htm&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0swCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=c2bc3e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rthk9.rthk.hk/chiculture/chilit/dy01_0205.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d35c8ec5677c45822d1e26aad677f7b7c21bfebe","tid":1519786,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0swCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=36e4af5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n